text.title: Current Totals
text.short: Current total number of variants, genes, phenotypes, interpretations, variant types.
text.long: ClinVar annotations include gene symbols, phenotypic data, interpretations and variant types. Please see the ClinVar website for deep details. The graph here shows how a simple computer algorithm would count the number of unique identifiers.

metadata.author: Bret Heale
metadata.notes: TSV is based on most current version. Each version of ClinVar is DISTINCT! Later versions can even have variants with submission dates that pre-date ClinVar!
